text: Innherreds Avis (The Innherred Gazette) was a Norwegian newspaper published in Steinkjer from December 2, 1933 to June 26, 1934. Innherreds avis.Høeg, Tom Arbo. 1974. Norske aviser: Registerbind. Oslo: Universitetsbibliotekets Hustrykkeri, p. 89. The editor for this entire period was Reidar Stavseth. ==References== Category:Defunct newspapers published in Norway Category:Norwegian-language newspapers Category:Mass media in Trøndelag Category:Publications established in 1933 Category:Publications disestablished in 1934
